jeigen
Class DenseMatrix

java.lang.Object
  jeigen.DenseMatrix

public class DenseMatrix
extends java.lang.Object

A dense matrix. This is faster than SparseMatrixLil for fully dense matrices. SparseMatrixLil will be faster if much of the matrix is zeros.
